data.name: Spotify Clone
data.description: A Spotify Clone web application built using HTML5 and CSS3. Developed a responsive music player interface focusing on UI/UX design to mimic Spotify's layout, enhancing front-end styling proficiency.

data.name: Simon Says
data.description: A web-based Simon Says memory game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This game challenges players to remember and reproduce an increasingly long sequence of colors, testing memory and focus. Created to practice DOM manipulation, event handling, and game logic in JavaScript.

data.name: Side Mini Projects
data.description: A collection of basic mini projects built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. These projects focus on practicing core web development concepts such as layouts, styling, DOM manipulation, and interactive features, designed to strengthen problem-solving and front-end development skills.
